name: Rg-cqb-killhouse.vr
tagline: RG Killhouse built by RG(Reality Gamer) member - aBrat. Aiming to create the best CQC, or CQB however you prefere to call it, ground to train and have fun at the same time
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
Welcome to the RG CQB Killhouse GitHub page. Here you can find the full version, which will be updated constantly in order to fix, add or migrate it in RG Modpack. If you have any questions do not hesistate to conntact the Author personaly.
Aswel make shure to check out the [RG website](https://realitygamer.org/) and join the comunity yourself.
Best of wishes.

### Authors and Contributors
Author of the CQB Killhouse is @aBrat, current contributors are @RG-Helios and @aBrat
Our work together will help create the best CQB enviroment to train and have fun in whatever section the person is from.

### Support or Contact
You want to join the RG and be able to play the CQB Training ground aswel ? Check this [link](https://realitygamer.org/)
